data.description: Welcome to this beautiful cape cod home in Bayview Beach! Situated in an established, quiet neighborhood, this home is a must-see! With wood floors throughout the downstairs, a large open family room with a wood burning fireplace and tons of natural light, you will immediately fall in love the charm of this home. Enjoy nights on your screened porch or entertaining in the spacious front and back yards. On the main level, you will find 2 bedrooms and a full bath, plus another 2 bedrooms and full bath upstairs with a loft area large enough for an office space. All bedrooms are spacious and feature walk in closets. The kitchen has been updated with shaker cabinets and granite countertops, and of course it has a much desired pantry! Lots of storage throughout including easy attic access. Gas line to the house was run by the city, so the home can easily be plumbed for gas if desired. Window treatments, W/D convey. Don't miss this one!
